  + [parent_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_boundary_faculty_inspection_runtime
  + [child_frame_set] is manager_state, empty_ready_task_set, blocked_task_set, operating_loop_tick_026, user_direction_boundary, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is boundary_faculty_inspection.py, 2026-06-24_task_060_boundary_faculty_inspection_runtime_001.hg.sop, Manager_State.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_026.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is recognize empty ReadyTaskSet and preserve blocked boundaries
  + [question_register] is whether to create new SOP slices, review blocked tasks, configure remote policy, or wait for user direction without inventing ready work
  + [delineation_register] is inside empty ReadyTaskSet, completed Task_146, blocked Task_004, blocked Task_040, focal state, registry state, outside, and commit cadence
  + [periphery_register] is worker mutation outside, branch creation outside, remote sync outside, hidden-state replay outside, unrelated dirty files outside, credentials outside, and destructive action outside
  + [operation_register] is validate_boundary_runtime, update_manager_empty_queue, commit, push, notify_no_ready_tasks
  + [evidence_register] is Manager_State completed Task_146, Boundary Faculty Inspection runtime, generated boundary inspection graph, and operating_loop_tick_026
  + [wisdom_register] is Codex should stop at the empty ready queue boundary rather than manufacturing implementation work
  + [caution_register] is blocked tasks require external remote policy, credentials, or user direction before action
  + [balance_register] is stable because Task_060 completed with tests and separate Honesty/Security boundary fault outputs visible
  + [integration_register] is Task_060 completed and no ready local runtime tasks remain
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, broad local-worker readiness, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

